; Audi A4 (8D)
;
; Component: J220 - Engine (#01) - AFC (2.8l 12V)
;
; P/N: 8D0-906-266-?
;
; See special notes on this Ecu:
;
; http://www.ross-tech.com/vag-com/audi_issues.html#HitachiOBD2
;
; Readiness Status via Generic OBD-2 (Binary Data in MVB 029)
;
; created on 01/Dec/2010 by Dana Smetanick (Dana@Ross-Tech.com)
; updated on 28/Jan/2011 by Dana Smetanick (Dana@Ross-Tech.com) / added Coding
; updated on 31/Jan/2011 by Sebastian Stange (Sebastian@Ross-Tech.com)
;
; requires VCDS 10.6.3 or newer
;
;
;---------------------------------------------------
;
; measuring blocks & basic setting
;
;---------------------------------------------------
;
;
001,0,Note: Only run one group at a time on this ECU
001,1,Engine Coolant, temperature, ECT (G62)
001,2,MAF sensor, output voltage 
001,3,Altitude, only w/SAI
001,4,ECM voltage
;
002,0,Throttle position sensor
002,1,TPS (G69) Coarse, Idle to WOT range, Specification: 0.250...4.750 V 
002,2,TPS (G69) Fine, Idle && Lower, Partial throttle range: 0.250...1.275 V
002,3,TPS (G69),Learning value, Specification: 0.250...0.500 V
002,4,Closed Throttle, switch (F60), Specification: Open = 0 Closed = 1
;
003,0,Note: Only run one group at a time on this ECU
003,1,Engine speed, (RPM)
003,2,Engine load
003,3,Throttle angle
003,4,Vehicle speed
;
004,0,IAC && ASC Learning
004,1,Idle Air Control, valve (IAC)
004,2,Idle Speed, Control learning
004,3,Idle Speed, Control learning
;
005,0,Oxygen Sensor Learning Bank 1
005,1,O2s Learning,at Idle
005,2,O2s Learning,Part Throttle I
005,3,O2s Learning,Part Throttle II
005,4,O2s Learning,Part Throttle III
;
006,0,Oxygen Sensor Learning  Bank 2
006,1,O2s Learning,at Idle
006,2,O2s Learning,Part Throttle I
006,3,O2s Learning,Part Throttle II
006,4,O2s Learning,Part Throttle III
;
007,0,Oxygen Sensor Control Bank 1
007,1,O2s Control,, Specification: 0.0 +/- 6.0 %
007,2,O2s Learning, Range
007,3,O2s Learning, Diagnosis
007,4,O2s Learning, Display
;
008,0,Oxygen Sensor Control Bank 2
008,1,O2s Control,, Specification: 0.0 +/- 6.0 %,
008,2,O2s Learning, Range
008,3,O2s Learning, Diagnosis
008,4,O2s Learning, Display
;
009,0,Note: Only run one group at a time on this ECU
009,1,O2s Control, Bank 1
009,2,O2s Control, Bank 2
009,3,Evap Sol.(N80), Duty Cycle
009,4,Throttle angle
;
010,0,Oxygen Sensor
010,1,O2s Control, Bank 1, and momentary O2s learning value
010,2,O2s Control, Bank 2, and momentary O2s learning value
010,3,Heated O2s, Bank 1, control Voltage
010,4,Heated O2s, Bank 2, control Voltage
;
011,1,Ignition Timing,, w/o knock or idle speed control
011,2,Ignition Timing,, with knock and idle speed control
011,3,Ignition Timing, Access to ISC, Idle Speed Control
011,4,Closed Throttle, Position switch 
;
012,0,Note: Only run one group at a time on this ECU
012,1,Engine Speed
012,2,Engine Load
012,3,Ignition Timing,Map switching
012,4,Ignition Timing,,Retarded by knock control
;
