;
;
;---------------------------------------------------
;
; coding
;
;---------------------------------------------------
;
;
C00,Engine Electronics (J220) Coding
C01,??xxx: Country/Emission
C02,01 = Exhaust Gas Recirculation and Evaporative Emissions Sensor (G172)
C03,10 = Exhaust Gas Recirculation / Evaporative Emissions Sensor (G172) and Secondary Air Injection (SAI)
C04,xx?xx: Drive/Additional Functions
C05,0 = Front-Wheel-Drive w/o Traction Control (ASR)
C06,1 = Front-Wheel-Drive with Traction Control (ASR)
C07,2 = All-Wheel-Drive w/o Traction Control (ASR)
C08,xxx?x: Transmission
C09,0 = 5-Speed Manual Transmission
C10,3 = 4 Speed Automatic Transmission (01N)
C11,4 = 4 Speed Automatic Transmission (01F/01K - HP-18)
C12,5 = 5 Speed Automatic Transmission (01V)
C13,xxxx?: Vehicle Type
C14,1 = B-Class (e.g. Audi A4)
C15,2 = C-Class (e.g. Audi A6)
C16,4 = Special (e.g. Audi Cabriolet)
;
